cs.CR, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.DC 

The paper discusses a security threat (Rowhammer) to cloud servers and proposes a methodology to test for vulnerability. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), computer architecture (cs.AR), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper involves testing and analysis of hardware components (DRAM), which could place it in the categories of software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
